  "title": "1 Year Contract KYC Analyst – Private Banking_BJJ",
  "description": "<p>1 Year Contract KYC Analyst – Private Banking</p><p><br />Our client is a bank.</p><p><br />Job Description:</p><p>•\tSupport Front Office to complete the periodic reviews for Private Wealth clients</p><p>•\tReview client’s profile during periodic review to ensure conformity to internal and regulatory requirements on AML/CFT/CDD standards</p><p>•\tConduct periodic reviews, due diligence and transaction monitoring processes to ensure compliance with rules, regulations, and KYC requirements</p><p>•\tProduce client risk assessments, due diligence analysis and assign an appropriate risk rating</p><p>•\tAccurately identify gaps (if any) in client's source of wealth</p><p>•\tLiaise with relationship managers for deficiencies of KYC information and obtain relevant documentation</p><p>•\tEnsure name screening alerts are handled according to guidelines and procedures</p><p><br />Job Requirements:</p><p>•\tDiploma or Degree in any relevant discipline</p><p>•\t4 to 8 years of relevant SOW/Compliance/KYC/CDD experience</p><p>•\tSalary ranges between S$5,000 to S$8,000 per month</p><p><br />Please send your application directly via janntan@recruitexpress.com.sg for a faster response.</p><p><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br />(Jann) Tan Wei Ying (R1103708)</p><p>Email Address: janntan@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p>Recruiter's Ref Code: #BJJ</p>",
